<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">place-self</code> å±æ€§æ˜¯ <code class="highlighter-rouge">align-self</code> å±æ€§å’Œ <code class="highlighter-rouge">justify-self</code> å±æ€§çš„åˆå¹¶ç®€å†™å½¢å¼ã€‚</p>

